# VEHICLE::GET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL

## Summary
Gets the vehicles dirt level 0.0 (clean) to 15.9 (dirty)

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Dirt level does not become greater than 15.0
